// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1887 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: eb6a1a30-2abf-5f22-a845-8113ed6fcf51

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
